extends layout

block content
    nav.navbar.navbar-default.navbar-static
        div.container
            div.row
                div.col-xs-10.col-sm-7.col-md-7.col-lg-6.title
                    h1.lightblue Let's ask 
                    h1 The Guardian Hivemind
                    p.subheader.lightblue Left-wing headline soup. Freshly regurgitated.
                div#navbar.col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-md-5.col-lg-5
                    //- div.navopt.section
                    //-     input(placeholder="Enter a tag")
                    div.navopt.search
                        p What do you think about...
                        input#question.input-block(type="text", class="form-control", placeholder='')
                        button.btn.btn-primary#search Ask
                        button.btn.btn-primary#openOptions
                            i.fa.fa-angle-down
                        select#section.input-block.optional.closed.form-control
                            option(value="all") All sections
                            option(value="commentisfree") Comment is Free
                            option(value="news") News
                            option(value="politics") Politics
                            option(value="world") World
                            option(value="culture") Culture
                            option(value="business") Economy
                            option(value="environment") Environment
                            option(value="technology") Technology
                        input#to-date.input-block.optional.closed.datepicker(type="text", class="form-control", data-date-format="yyyy-mm-dd", placeholder='#{today}', value='#{today}')
    div.article-wrap.articles  
        div.articles.overlay.col-xs-12.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.col-lg-6.col-lg-offset-3
            div.articles.topbar
                div.col-xs-10 
                    h3 Articles
                div.col-xs-2
                    button.btn#closeArticles
                        span.glyphicon.glyphicon-remove
            div.articles.article-box
    div.info-box
        div.article-wrap
            div.overlay.col-xs-12.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.col-lg-6.col-lg-offset-3
                div.topbar
                    div.col-xs-10
                         h3 Info
                    div.col-xs-2
                        button.btn#closeInfo
                            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-remove
                div.article-box This pointless web app was designed and built by me, Jon King, with the help of a few well-known libraries. It's basically a simple Express app built with NodeJS, cached with MongoDB, parsing requests to the Guardian's API and feeding them back to you to be sprayed onto your screens and end up as a little puddle of psychedelic journalism. You can see all the intimate details here -
                    a(href="https://github.com/JonathanUsername/ask-the-guardian-hivemind")  on the Github page
    div.canvas-holder
        canvas#cloudCanvas
    div.info#openInfo
        i.fa.fa-info-circle